item.title: The G35 experience
item.description: Some of you might be thinking of a top secret Logitech product. I know I was when I heard the utterance “G35.” The G35 is a pretty sweet car and thanks to Donnie, in sales, I was lucky enough to get my first ride in one today. I have noticed that a lot of people here in Texas own a G35. Back home no one has one. In fact, I saw my first one when I arrived in Dallas.
